WEBVTT

00:02.170 --> 00:03.671
[ Man ]
IN 1979, CONGRESS AUTHORIZED...

00:03.704 --> 00:06.140
THE FORMATION OF
A CONTINGENT OF ELITE
SPECIAL FORCES SOLDIERS...

00:06.174 --> 00:09.643
WHO ANSWER
ONLY TO THE PRESIDENT
OF THE UNITED STATES.

00:09.677 --> 00:13.314
THEIR MISSIONS,
AND THEIR VERY EXISTENCE,
ARE CLOSELY GUARDED SECRETS,

00:13.347 --> 00:15.316
PROTECTED BY
THE SOLDIERS THEMSELVES...

00:15.349 --> 00:18.018
AND THEIR WIVES,
WHO POSSESS SECRETS
OF THEIR OWN.

00:23.357 --> 00:25.559
[ Barking ]

00:45.613 --> 00:47.648
[ Groans ]

01:05.733 --> 01:07.468
[ Dog Barking ]

01:13.474 --> 01:16.644
[ Men Shouting
In Foreign Language ]

01:18.812 --> 01:21.682
[ Speaking Foreign Language ]

01:25.686 --> 01:27.488
[ Foreign Language ]

01:31.525 --> 01:35.095
OKAY, MACK.
YOU AND CARLITO,
GET THE PRISONERS OUT.

01:35.129 --> 01:36.964
THIRTY-MINUTE CHOW
AND COMFORT BREAK.
LET'S DO IT.

01:36.997 --> 01:39.133
CAN DO EASY, G.I.

01:41.001 --> 01:43.504
[ Speaking Foreign Language ]

02:08.496 --> 02:10.631
THANK YOU.

02:10.664 --> 02:12.366
YOU'RE WELCOME.

02:32.586 --> 02:35.523
THE PASS IS BLOCKED.

02:35.556 --> 02:38.726
I COUNT 12 MEN
AND A LIGHT MACHINE GUN.
WHICH WAY THEY ORIENTED?

02:38.759 --> 02:40.461
- THIS WAY.
- CONFIGURATION?

02:40.494 --> 02:42.963
OVERWATCH, GOOD DISPERSAL.
MACHINE GUN HAS GOOD
FIELD OF FIRE.

02:42.996 --> 02:45.466
- THEY KNOW WHAT THEY'RE DOING.
- VEHICLES?

02:45.499 --> 02:48.802
- COUPLE OF TRUCKS. ONE'S
A PICKUP. OTHER'S A TWO TON.
- [ Sighs ]

02:48.836 --> 02:51.038
DIRT DIVER.

02:55.008 --> 02:58.979
- PRINCIPAL ROUTE IS BLOCKED.
- THAT'S THE ONLY WAY ACROSS
THE BORDER TO BASE CAMP.

02:59.012 --> 03:01.849
- HOW ABOUT WE DETOUR NORTH,
MAKE THE CROSSING HERE?
- WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH FUEL...

03:01.882 --> 03:03.684
TO MAKE IT THAT FAR.

03:03.717 --> 03:08.088
AS LONG AS THESE DAMN SUNSPOTS
LAST, WE CAN'T MAKE RADIO
CONTACT FOR A RESUPPLY DROP.

03:08.121 --> 03:09.823
THAT SMALL
FORWARD SUPPORT BASE.

03:09.857 --> 03:13.261
THE ONE THEY SET UP FOR
THE SWEEP THE 101st WAS
MAKING ALONG THE BORDER.

03:13.294 --> 03:15.596
THEY SHOULD STILL
BE IN POSITION.

03:15.629 --> 03:18.766
WELL, IT'S A TEMPORARY SITE
FOR RESUPPLY.
THERE'S NOT VERY MUCH THERE.

03:18.799 --> 03:22.903
BUT THEY'LL HAVE FUEL AND
A SECURITY DETACHMENT. WE CAN
GO TO GROUND, WAIT THIS OUT.

03:22.936 --> 03:26.139
- BETTER THAN NOTHIN'.
- I'LL PLAN US A ROUTE.

03:29.477 --> 03:31.645
CHAI. CHAI.

03:34.815 --> 03:37.050
CHAI.

03:41.755 --> 03:43.857
WILLIAMS WILL BE BACK SOON.

03:43.891 --> 03:46.994
WE GOTTA GET PREPARED
TO GET OUT OF HERE--
THIS TEA IS VERY GOOD.

03:48.962 --> 03:50.764
I'M GLAD YOU APPROVE.

03:50.798 --> 03:54.101
OF COURSE, IT WOULD BE MUCH
BETTER IF YOU WERE MY GUESTS
IN MY VILLAGE.

03:54.134 --> 03:56.169
MY WIFE MAKES A SUPERIOR TEA.

03:57.838 --> 03:59.640
YOUR ENGLISH IS VERY GOOD.

04:01.141 --> 04:03.944
[ Foreign Word ]
TRULY?

04:03.977 --> 04:06.246
I ASSURE YOU.

04:06.980 --> 04:09.583
SIR, I THANK YOU
FOR THESE MEALS,

04:09.617 --> 04:12.486
BUT NOW I WOULD KNOW WHAT
YOU ARE DOING CREEPING THROUGH
MY COUNTRY AT NIGHT,

04:12.520 --> 04:15.055
KIDNAPPING HONEST MEN
FROM THEIR BEDS.

04:15.088 --> 04:16.757
THERE ARE PEOPLE
WHO WISH TO SPEAK WITH YOU.

04:16.790 --> 04:19.460
AND THIS IS THEIR FORM
OF INVITATION?

04:19.493 --> 04:22.496
TO SEND YOU AND YOUR MEN
TO STEAL US FROM OUR HOMES,

04:22.530 --> 04:25.333
TO TERRIFY OUR FAMILIES,
TO KILL OUR KINSMEN?

04:25.366 --> 04:27.968
THIS IS CIVILIZED BEHAVIOR?
THIS IS HONEST DISCOURSE?

04:28.001 --> 04:29.737
IS IT CIVILIZED
TO BOMB INNOCENT PEOPLE?

04:29.770 --> 04:31.972
MOST CERTAINLY NOT.

04:32.005 --> 04:34.107
WELL, THERE'S A WAR GOING ON,

04:34.141 --> 04:36.577
AND THESE PEOPLE WISH TO SPEAK
WITH YOU ABOUT CERTAIN THINGS.

04:36.610 --> 04:39.947
AND THEY THINK I KNOW ABOUT
THESE CERTAIN THINGS?

04:39.980 --> 04:43.183
- SUPPOSEDLY SO.
- COULD WE HAVE SOME MORE TEA?

04:56.229 --> 05:01.201
SIR, HAVE YOU SEEN ME OR ANY
OF MY PEOPLE IN YOUR COUNTRY
WAGING THIS WAR YOU SPEAK OF?

05:01.234 --> 05:03.704
PEOPLE HAVE ATTACKED MY COUNTRY.

05:03.737 --> 05:05.973
MY PEOPLE HAVE
ATTACKED YOUR COUNTRY?

05:06.006 --> 05:08.376
MEN FROM MY VILLAGE,
MY TRIBE, MY CLAN...

05:08.409 --> 05:11.044
HAVE COME TO YOUR COUNTRY
AND ATTACKED YOUR PEOPLE?

05:11.078 --> 05:13.614
SIR, WHEN DID THIS
VILE EVENT TAKE PLACE?

05:13.647 --> 05:15.616
OTHERS LIKE YOU HAVE DONE SO.

05:15.649 --> 05:17.685
I SEE.

05:19.152 --> 05:21.822
MEN WHO LIVE IN HOUSES
MADE OF MUD AND STONE--

05:21.855 --> 05:25.459
SIMPLE MEN WHO
SPEND THEIR LIVES TENDING
THEIR FLOCKS AND FIELDS.

05:25.493 --> 05:29.730
MEN SUCH AS THESE
HAVE ATTACKED THE MOST POWERFUL
NATION IN THE WORLD?

05:29.763 --> 05:31.331
IT HAS HAPPENED.

05:31.365 --> 05:33.567
SIR, I THINK YOU ARE
A VERY FEARFUL PEOPLE.

05:33.601 --> 05:35.636
I THINK YOU ARE BEING MISLED.

05:35.669 --> 05:38.372
WHY DO YOU NOT RELEASE US?

05:38.406 --> 05:42.643
THEN WE CAN RETURN TO OUR HOMES.
AND YOU SHOULD DO LIKEWISE.

05:42.676 --> 05:47.147
- I HAVE A JOB TO DO.
- AND YOU DO THIS JOB
WITHOUT THOUGHT?

05:47.180 --> 05:50.684
HUH? WITHOUT CONSCIENCE?
WHAT SORT OF MAN
ACTS IN THIS MANNER?

05:52.420 --> 05:54.588
I'M A SOLDIER.

05:54.622 --> 05:57.491
THAT IS NOT AN ANSWER.

05:57.525 --> 06:00.628
BOSS, TAKE A LOOK
AT OUR BACK TRAIL.

06:09.570 --> 06:12.205
LET'S MOUNT UP.

06:24.284 --> 06:26.053
[ Shouts ]

06:28.489 --> 06:30.691
STOP! DO NOT SHOOT!

06:30.724 --> 06:32.225
I WILL TALK TO HIM.

06:32.259 --> 06:36.096
[ Foreign Language ]

06:45.639 --> 06:48.476
THIS CAN BE AVOIDED.
RELEASE US
AND SAVE YOURSELVES.

06:48.509 --> 06:52.245
FROM WHO?
FROM THOSE
WHO WILL SURELY COME.

06:52.279 --> 06:55.115
WHO AND HOW MANY?
YOUR CLAN IS A SMALL ONE.

06:55.148 --> 06:58.185
BUT MY TRIBE IS LEGION.

07:01.855 --> 07:04.525
- IN THE TRUCK.
- SO BE IT.

07:06.426 --> 07:08.428
[ Sighs ]

07:21.942 --> 07:24.144
MOVE OUT.

07:44.331 --> 07:46.166
[ Gunshots ]

07:47.901 --> 07:50.170
[ Gunshots Continue ]

07:55.809 --> 07:58.011
WE GOT ANOTHER ONE WITH US!

07:58.045 --> 08:00.313
ROGER THAT!

08:05.653 --> 08:09.790
SUPPORT BASE OCEAN CEILING.
THIS IS TEAM ANACONDA.

08:09.823 --> 08:11.625
OCEAN CEILING,
THIS IS TEAM ANACONDA.

08:11.659 --> 08:16.229
WE ARE NEARING YOUR LOCATION
WITH HOSTILE FORCE IN PURSUIT.

08:16.263 --> 08:18.431
[ Gunshots Continue ]

08:20.033 --> 08:24.137
SUPPORT BASE OCEAN CEILING.
THIS IS TEAM ANACONDA.

08:24.171 --> 08:26.807
MY TEAM CONSISTS
OF TWO VEHICLES.

08:26.840 --> 08:30.978
I WILL FLASH YOU THE VISUAL
FRIENDLY SIGNAL
WHEN WE COME IN SIGHT.

08:31.011 --> 08:34.481
GO TO 100% SECURITY.
I AUTHENTICATE.

08:34.514 --> 08:36.416
GOLF SHOE. OVER.

08:45.793 --> 08:48.762
SWING LEFT, 30 DEGREES.

08:48.796 --> 08:51.231
HOLD ON!

08:53.300 --> 08:57.137
- HOW FAR TO THE CAMP?
- IT'S JUST BEHIND
THAT FIELD MASS.

09:00.808 --> 09:02.876
OCEAN CEILING,
THIS IS TEAM ANACONDA.

09:02.910 --> 09:05.545
OCEAN CEILING,
THIS IS TEAM ANACONDA.

09:05.579 --> 09:07.615
OVER.

09:07.648 --> 09:09.583
NO GOOD. RADIO'S DEAD.

09:12.552 --> 09:15.222
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

09:15.255 --> 09:17.224
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

09:17.257 --> 09:19.760
* HERE WE GO
ON THE ROAD *

09:19.793 --> 09:22.029
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

09:22.062 --> 09:24.231
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

09:24.264 --> 09:27.134
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP **

09:33.741 --> 09:36.276
[ Gunshots ]

09:47.520 --> 09:49.957
[ Gunshots ]

09:49.990 --> 09:52.626
- [ Man ]
THAT SOUND LIKE GUNFIRE?
- [ Man #2 ] GUNFIRE! GUNFIRE!

09:52.660 --> 09:54.728
GUNFIRE!
[ All Shouting ]

09:54.762 --> 09:57.998
GO! GO, GO, GO!

09:58.031 --> 10:01.101
I SEE IT! JONAS!
JONAS, UP AHEAD! THE CAMP!

10:01.134 --> 10:03.170
[ Jonas ]
KEEP GOING!

10:06.206 --> 10:09.442
JONAS! JONAS, THE CAMP!
THEY'RE FIRING ON US!

10:21.488 --> 10:24.624
- [ Man ]
THE ONE ON THE LEFT.
- [ Man #2 ] I GOT 'EM.

10:24.658 --> 10:26.927
HOLD! HOLD!

10:26.960 --> 10:29.229
THAT FIRST TRUCK IS FRIENDLY!
SWITCH FIRE!

10:33.133 --> 10:35.468
- [ Shouts ]
- [ Mack ]
WE TOOK ONE.

10:40.473 --> 10:41.574
GO, GO, GO, GO, GO!

11:00.994 --> 11:03.663
[ Mack ]
GREY, GET OVER HERE NOW,
DAMN IT!

11:03.697 --> 11:05.532
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

11:10.103 --> 11:12.740
[ Man Shouting
In Foreign Language ]

11:12.773 --> 11:15.042
[ All Shouting
In Foreign Language ]

11:17.677 --> 11:19.179
[ Groans ]

11:42.469 --> 11:45.138
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

11:50.878 --> 11:53.646
[ Machine Gun Fire In Distance ]

11:56.784 --> 11:58.685
SARGE! SARGE!

11:58.718 --> 12:00.287
I THOUGHT--
NOT NOW.

12:00.320 --> 12:02.455
- WHO'S IN CHARGE HERE?
- WHO WANTS TO KNOW?

12:02.489 --> 12:04.591
I'M LIEUTENANT BAILEY,
CAMP COMMANDER. AND YOU?

12:04.624 --> 12:07.027
BLANE, SERGEANT MAJOR,
SPECIAL OPS COMMAND.

12:07.060 --> 12:10.463
I'VE GOT SOME PRISONERS
THAT I NEED TO TURN OVER
TO MY HEADQUARTERS.

12:10.497 --> 12:12.599
UH, SERGEANT MAJOR,
THIS IS A LOG BASE.

12:12.632 --> 12:14.968
- I'M AFRAID I CAN'T TAKE
PRISONERS OFF YOUR HANDS.
- COMFORTABLE IN THERE?

12:15.002 --> 12:17.104
LEAVE THE PRISONERS ALONE.

12:17.137 --> 12:19.907
- LIEUTENANT, TELL YOUR MEN
TO GET AWAY FROM MY PRISONERS.
- [ Man ] COME ON OUT.

12:19.940 --> 12:22.042
GET AWAY FROM THERE,
YOU KNOTHEADS!

12:22.075 --> 12:25.913
- [ Man ]
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT?
- HEY! BACK TO YOUR POSITIONS.

12:25.946 --> 12:28.481
SORRY, SERGEANT MAJOR.

12:28.515 --> 12:31.484
THIS IS THE CLOSEST THEY'VE
EVER BEEN TO LIVE HAJJIS.

12:31.518 --> 12:34.087
[ Jonas ]
LIEUTENANT, YOU SHOULD GET
YOUR TROOPS BACK HERE.

12:34.121 --> 12:36.256
THE GROUND IS CRAWLING
WITH MILITIA.

12:36.289 --> 12:39.960
I'M IN CHARGE OF SECURITY
HERE, SERGEANT MAJOR.
THOSE ARE MY REACTION TEAM,

12:39.993 --> 12:42.395
WHO NOT ONLY COVERED
YOUR OUTFIT...

12:42.429 --> 12:44.464
BUT ARE CAPABLE OF
TAKING CARE OF THEMSELVES.

12:44.497 --> 12:46.967
NO DOUBT.
BUT GIVE THEM
THE RECALL.

12:47.000 --> 12:49.036
THEY DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S OUT THERE.

12:50.537 --> 12:54.441
BLAYLOCK, RAISE
SERGEANT MORALES ON THE RADIO.

12:54.474 --> 12:56.643
TELL HIM TO TURN BACK.
WHAT IF I CAN'T--

12:56.676 --> 12:59.847
JUST DO WHAT I SAY!

12:59.880 --> 13:03.851
MA'AM, I NEED A PLACE TO HOLD
THE PRISONERS UNTIL I CAN
TURN THEM OVER.

13:03.884 --> 13:05.953
YOU GOT A SECURE SPOT FOR THAT?

13:05.986 --> 13:09.422
UH, THERE'S THE SENSITIVE
ITEMS CAGE IN THE LOG AREA.
IT'S IN THE CENTER OF CAMP.

13:09.456 --> 13:12.625
THAT SHOULD DO. UH, CHAMBERS,
SHOW THESE MEN THE CAGE.

13:12.659 --> 13:14.962
ON YOUR FEET, SOLDIER,

13:14.995 --> 13:17.630
WHEN AN OFFICER SPEAKS TO YOU!

13:17.664 --> 13:20.667
SERGEANT GERHARDT,
TAKE THE PRISONERS TO THE CAGE.

13:20.700 --> 13:23.303
PUT A GUARD ON THEM.
DONE.

13:23.336 --> 13:25.672
LET'S GO, HERO.
SHOW ME THE HOOSEGOW.

13:25.705 --> 13:28.675
MA'AM, IS THERE A PLACE
WHERE ME AND YOU CAN TALK?
YEAH.

13:34.481 --> 13:37.517
OH. NOTHING AS GOOD
AS A BAD CUP OF ARMY COFFEE.

13:37.550 --> 13:40.620
THE WORST.
[ Chuckles ]
I GREW UP ON IT.

13:40.653 --> 13:44.291
- ARMY BRAT, HUH?
- YEAH. DAD WAS AN ARTILLERY
FIRST SERGEANT.

13:44.324 --> 13:46.526
[ Static ]
I KNOW FORT SILL...

13:46.559 --> 13:48.561
LIKE MOST WOMEN
KNOW THEIR
OWN KITCHEN.

13:48.595 --> 13:51.198
A DIVIDED COMMAND
IS A DEAD COMMAND, LIEUTENANT.

13:51.231 --> 13:54.101
WHAT WOULD DAD DO IF
HE WAS HERE IN YOUR POSITION?

13:55.435 --> 13:57.504
HE'D TAKE CHARGE.

13:57.537 --> 14:00.507
- THEN DO IT.
- I ONLY HAVE MY SUPPLY
AND SUPPORT TROOPS.

14:00.540 --> 14:04.744
JUST SIX OF THEM.
WALLACE HAS THE INFANTRY PLATOON
CHARGED WITH CAMP SECURITY.

14:04.777 --> 14:07.047
AND, WELL--
[ Chuckles ]
YOU KNOW WHAT KIND OF A UNIT...

14:07.080 --> 14:09.416
IS SENT OUT
AS A DETACHMENT.
MM-HMM.

14:09.449 --> 14:12.920
THEY SENT YOU ALL THEIR BUMS.
A BUNCH OF MALCONTENTS WITH
A PISS-POOR SERGEANT IN CHARGE.

14:12.953 --> 14:15.555
BUT WALLACE
IS SUBORDINATE TO YOU.

14:15.588 --> 14:17.991
YOU'RE THE ONE IN COMMAND.
HE DOESN'T BELIEVE IT.

14:18.025 --> 14:21.094
- 'CAUSE YOU DON'T EITHER.
- LOOK, HE DRAGS HIS FEET
ON EVERYTHING I TELL HIM.

14:21.128 --> 14:23.096
YOU ACT LIKE AN OFFICER,
HE'LL ACT LIKE AN N.C.O.

14:23.130 --> 14:26.533
- HE DOESN'T HAVE TO LIKE IT.
HE JUST HAS TO DO IT.
- [ Static On Radio ]

14:26.566 --> 14:30.270
[ Man On Radio ]
...HIT. WE'VE BEEN OUTFLANKED.
HE DIDN'T RECALL THAT PATROL.

14:30.303 --> 14:32.172
WE'VE GOT HOSTILES
CLOSIN' IN ON US.
MORALES IS DEAD!

14:32.205 --> 14:34.107
[ Machine Gun Fire
Continues ]
A .50-CALIBER--

14:34.141 --> 14:36.609
MORALES IS DEAD.
WE NEED IMMEDIATE FIRE--

14:36.643 --> 14:39.879
ALL RIGHT. YOU TWO, IN THE
TRUCK. GET YOUR ASSES IN THERE
NOW. YOU TOO, BLAYLOCK!

14:39.913 --> 14:41.881
HOLD IT. NOBODY GOES OUT.

14:41.915 --> 14:45.953
- THOSE ARE MY MEN IN THERE.
- AND NOW THEY'RE DEAD.
OR THEY'RE PLAYING DEAD.

14:45.986 --> 14:48.788
BUT IF YOU GO OUT THERE,
YOU'RE JUST GONNA ADD
TO THE BODY COUNT.

14:48.821 --> 14:53.126
DAMN IT,
I AM NOT GONNA JUST SIT HERE AND
WATCH AS MY MEN SIT OUT THERE--

14:53.160 --> 14:55.929
YOU BE AT EASE, SERGEANT!

14:55.963 --> 14:59.933
I TOLD YOU TO RECALL THOSE MEN.
BY NOW, HUNDREDS OF MILITIA
ARE SWARMING THOSE HILLS.

14:59.967 --> 15:02.602
THEY LURED YOUR MEN
INTO A HASTY AMBUSH.

15:02.635 --> 15:04.737
YOU FOLLOW NOW, AND THEY'LL DO
THE SAME TO YOU.

15:11.678 --> 15:13.746
OUT OF THE TRUCK, MEN.
BUT, SARGE--

15:13.780 --> 15:15.782
I SAID OUT OF
THE DAMN TRUCK NOW!

15:15.815 --> 15:18.318
GO BACK TO YOUR POSITIONS.

15:20.153 --> 15:23.623
BUT IT WAS YOU
WHO LURED THEM IN HERE ON US.

15:23.656 --> 15:27.494
YOU AND THOSE DAMN RAG-HEADS
OF YOURS GOT MY MEN KILLED.

15:27.527 --> 15:29.096
SERGEANT!

15:32.165 --> 15:34.968
- HOW MANY MACHINE GUNS YOU GOT?
- WHAT?

15:35.002 --> 15:36.836
MACHINE GUNS.
HOW MANY AND WHAT KIND?

15:36.869 --> 15:39.839
THE NORMAL COMPLEMENT
FOR AN INFANTRY PLATOON.

15:39.872 --> 15:41.541
.50-CALS?
GONE.

15:42.442 --> 15:44.777
OUT THERE.

15:44.811 --> 15:46.746
THEY WERE IN THE HUMVEE.

15:46.779 --> 15:50.217
I NEED TO SEE YOUR FIRE SUPPORT
OVERLAYS AND A COPY
OF YOUR BARRIER PLAN.

15:54.321 --> 15:57.157
IT'S NOT EXACTLY A FORMAL PLAN.

15:57.190 --> 15:59.959
IT'S MORE LIKE IN MY HEAD,
IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

15:59.993 --> 16:02.162
NO, SERGEANT,
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

16:02.195 --> 16:04.831
BUT WHAT I SEE IS THE RESULTS
OF COMPLACENCY...

16:04.864 --> 16:06.699
AND INACTION.

16:06.733 --> 16:09.002
WHAT'S THE FIRST PRIORITY
OF WORK IN THE DEFENSE?

16:12.305 --> 16:15.342
- UH, SECURITY.
- WELL, THERE'S NOT
MUCH HERE, IS THERE?

16:15.375 --> 16:18.011
BUT WE'RE GONNA CHANGE THAT.
AND WE'RE GONNA DO IT
IN A HURRY.

16:18.045 --> 16:21.348
AND YOU KNOW WHY.
BECAUSE COME SUNDOWN,

16:21.381 --> 16:24.651
ALL THOSE MEN ARE GONNA
TRY TO GET IN HERE.

16:24.684 --> 16:28.621
AND IF THEY GET INSIDE
THIS PERIMETER, THEY INTEND
TO KILL US ALL.

16:28.655 --> 16:30.423
IT IS AS SIMPLE AS THAT!

16:43.770 --> 16:47.874
OKAY, THEN.
THE LIEUTENANT WILL ISSUE
A DEFENSIVE ORDER MOST SKOSH.

16:47.907 --> 16:49.676
SERGEANT GERHARDT,

16:49.709 --> 16:53.646
GO WITH SERGEANT WALLACE
AND LAY OUT A TRIANGULAR
DEFENSIVE PERIMETER.

16:53.680 --> 16:57.050
AND WHEN THAT'S DONE, BOB,
SIGHT IN THE MACHINE GUNS.

16:57.084 --> 17:01.321
CARLITO, CHECK ON THE PRISONERS
AND GET 'EM UNDER COVER.

17:01.354 --> 17:04.591
THIS IS GONNA GET UGLY.
YEAH. WAY AHEAD OF YOU, TOP.
HECTOR'S ON IT NOW.

17:04.624 --> 17:07.594
- I'M GONNA HELP MACK WALK THE
"TRE," SEE WHAT WE GOT HERE.
- L.T.,

17:07.627 --> 17:09.096
A MOMENT.

17:13.133 --> 17:16.936
MACHINE GUNS IN PAIRS MUTUALLY
SUPPORTING HERE AND HERE.

17:16.969 --> 17:19.672
- YES, MA'AM.
- UNTIL EVENING STAND-TO,

17:19.706 --> 17:23.743
WE STAY AT 25% SECURITY,
WITH THE REST OF THE TROOPS
WORKING ON DEFENSIVE TASKS.

17:23.776 --> 17:25.778
100% SECURITY AT STAND-TO...

17:25.812 --> 17:28.181
AND 50% FOR THE DURATION
OF THE NIGHT.

17:28.215 --> 17:30.583
SERGEANT MAJOR, DIVIDE
YOUR TEAM AMONG THE SQUADS.

17:30.617 --> 17:34.621
AS THE SENIOR N.C.O. PRESENT,
I PLACE YOU IN CHARGE
OF THE DEFENSIVE WORK.

17:34.654 --> 17:37.624
ONCE YOU HAVE THE WORK
UNDER WAY, REPORT BACK TO ME.
YES, MA'AM.

17:37.657 --> 17:40.760
SERGEANT WALLACE, I'M GONNA
RECONFIGURE YOUR PLATOON.

17:40.793 --> 17:43.363
GIVE A SENIOR TEAM LEADER
AND ALL YOUR GRENADIERS
TO SERGEANT WILLIAMS.

17:43.396 --> 17:45.232
RIGHT. BAKER,

17:45.265 --> 17:47.400
GO WITH WILLIAMS AND
ROUND UP THE THUMPERS.

17:47.434 --> 17:50.470
[ Jonas ]
SERGEANT GREY,
TAKE A DETAIL OF TWO MEN...

17:50.503 --> 17:53.740
FROM EACH SQUAD AND GO TO WORK
ON THE BARRIER PLAN.

17:53.773 --> 17:55.875
WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH WIRE
TO COVER EVERYTHING IN DEPTH,

17:55.908 --> 17:58.745
SO PLUG THE NATURAL
AVENUES OF APPROACH.

17:58.778 --> 18:02.282
AND SHOVE THE WIRE THAT EXISTS
OUT PAST HAND GRENADE RANGE.

18:02.315 --> 18:05.585
WILCO.
YOU, COME WITH ME, MATE.

18:05.618 --> 18:08.621
WE DO THAT AND WE CAN'T
THROW OVER THE WIRE.

18:08.655 --> 18:12.992
THE MACHINE GUN--
FINAL PROTECTIVE LINE
COVERS THE WIRE.

18:13.025 --> 18:17.297
THIS WAY THE WIRE'S OUT FAR
ENOUGH THE ENEMY CAN'T THROW
HAND GRENADES IN ON US.

18:18.598 --> 18:20.900
I SEE.

18:20.933 --> 18:23.069
SERGEANT BROWN.
SIR.

18:23.102 --> 18:25.605
GATHER ALL FLARES
AND PLACE THEM IN THE C.P.

18:25.638 --> 18:29.142
WHEN YOU'VE DONE THAT, PUT
ANOTHER GUARD ON THE PRISONERS.
CONSIDER IT DONE.

18:30.977 --> 18:32.745
IT'S GONNA BE A LONG NIGHT.

18:32.779 --> 18:36.983
UNTIL THOSE RADIOS COME BACK
TO LIFE, WE'RE ON OUR OWN.

18:37.016 --> 18:39.118
NO CAVALRY'S COMING
TO THE RESCUE.
IT'S JUST US.

18:39.152 --> 18:41.254
BUT IF WE DIG IN DEEP...

18:41.288 --> 18:43.956
AND WORK HARD WITH
THE DAYLIGHT WE HAVE LEFT,

18:43.990 --> 18:46.159
I THINK EVERYTHING'LL
BE ALL RIGHT.

18:48.961 --> 18:51.464
[ Man ]
PUT YOUR BACK INTO IT!
LET'S GO!

18:51.498 --> 18:53.600
[ Chattering ]

18:53.633 --> 18:56.669
FIVE MORE CANS OVER HERE!
PRIMARY FIRING POSITIONS
ARE COMPLETE.

18:56.703 --> 18:58.538
AND THE BARRIERS
ARE ALMOST DONE.

18:58.571 --> 19:02.375
SERGEANT MAJOR,
I WANTED TO, UH--
TO THANK YOU--

19:02.409 --> 19:05.612
THE MEN ARE WORKING
ON THE SECONDARY POSITIONS.

19:05.645 --> 19:08.881
AS SOON AS THAT'S DONE,
WE'LL CONSTRUCT
THE FINAL FALLBACK.

19:08.915 --> 19:11.218
SERGEANT MAJOR, MA'AM,

19:11.251 --> 19:12.885
THE CONTAINERS ARE
IN POSITION AS YOU ORDERED.

19:12.919 --> 19:14.554
I'M GONNA TAKE THOSE--
[ Gunshots ]

19:16.756 --> 19:19.392
GOD ALMIGHTY!
IT'S OUR OWN .50-CALS
THEY'RE USING ON US!

19:19.426 --> 19:21.494
[ All Groaning ]

19:21.528 --> 19:24.464
- YOU GOTTA GET THOSE MEN
OUT OF THERE!
- MEDIC!

19:24.497 --> 19:26.999
WE NEED A MEDIC OUT HERE!
[ Wallace ]
YOU TWO!

19:27.033 --> 19:30.002
GET OVER HERE AND HELP US OUT!

19:30.036 --> 19:32.239
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

19:36.042 --> 19:37.310
WE GOTTA STOP THAT GUN.

19:37.344 --> 19:39.846
IT'S OUT OF RANGE OF ANYTHING
WE HAVE IN THE CAMP.

19:39.879 --> 19:43.583
- COME ON. COME ON.
- AND MY SNIPER RIFLES
ARE IN MY TRUCK.

19:43.616 --> 19:46.185
THE ONE OUT THERE.

19:48.955 --> 19:51.057
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

19:51.090 --> 19:54.361
CEASE FIRE!
YOU'RE JUST WASTING AMMO!

19:54.394 --> 19:57.264
THE LONG GUNS
ARE ON THE TRUCK, TOP.

19:57.297 --> 19:59.566
CAN'T OUR MACHINE GUNS
GIVE SUPPRESS FIRE?

19:59.599 --> 20:02.101
THE GUNS IN CAMP HAVE
AN EFFECTIVE RANGE
OF 1,100 METERS.

20:02.134 --> 20:04.371
THAT .50-CAL'S OUT THERE
AT TWO KLICKS.

20:04.404 --> 20:07.274
WE GOTTA GET THOSE LONG GUNS,
PUT THOSE GUYS
OUT OF ACTION.

20:07.307 --> 20:09.776
- THAT'S A LONG RUN.
- AIN'T GONNA GET NO SHORTER.

20:09.809 --> 20:11.978
WE CAN THROW SMOKE.

20:13.446 --> 20:15.448
HAVE AT IT.

20:23.323 --> 20:26.426
DUDE, THIS IS ONE OF THOSE
TIMES I LIKE BEING MY SIZE.

20:26.459 --> 20:29.629
WELL, THAT'S, LIKE,
YOUR OPINION, DUDE.

20:29.662 --> 20:31.331
[ Chuckles ]
LET'S GO.

20:36.303 --> 20:38.405
LET'S GO TOGETHER.
GIVE 'EM ONE TARGET
INSTEAD OF TWO.

20:38.438 --> 20:41.441
YOU WANT TO WAIT ON SMOKE?
WELL, WIND'S BLOWING
THE WRONG WAY,

20:41.474 --> 20:43.410
BUT IT MIGHT HOLD THEIR
ATTENTION FOR A SECOND.

20:43.443 --> 20:45.445
SMOKE!

20:53.820 --> 20:56.022
LET'S GO.

20:58.991 --> 21:01.694
MORE SMOKE!

21:19.646 --> 21:21.314
[ Grey Groans ]

21:25.017 --> 21:27.987
[ Foreign Language ]

21:33.025 --> 21:35.161
[ All Shouting ]

21:46.138 --> 21:48.174
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

21:52.579 --> 21:55.382
LIFE BECOMES
MORE INTERESTING, NO?

21:57.249 --> 22:00.387
I WAS JUST TELLING
MY FRIENDS HERE THAT LIFE
IS A GIFT FROM ALLAH.

22:00.420 --> 22:03.956
HE LENDS IT FOR A LITTLE
WHILE, THEN RECALLS IT
TO LEND TO SOMEONE ELSE.

22:03.990 --> 22:06.793
WELL, YOU CAN TALK
TO YOUR FRIENDS OUT THERE.
TELL THEM TO GO AWAY.

22:06.826 --> 22:09.295
COULD I?
[ Gunshot ]

22:09.328 --> 22:11.364
EVEN WERE IT SO,
WHY WOULD I WANT TO?

22:11.398 --> 22:15.034
TO SAVE LIVES.
TO PREVENT DEATH.

22:15.067 --> 22:17.236
WHY NOT RELEASE US
AND YOU GO AWAY?

22:17.269 --> 22:19.372
THAT WOULD PREVENT DEATH.

22:19.406 --> 22:21.207
CAN'T DO IT.

22:21.240 --> 22:23.309
THEN YOUR CHOICE IS DEATH.

22:23.342 --> 22:26.178
BUT WHO AMONG US
IS IMMORTAL? YOU?

22:26.212 --> 22:28.481
ME?
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

22:28.515 --> 22:30.316
NO.

22:30.349 --> 22:33.720
DEATH CLAIMS US ALL
AT THE APPROPRIATE TIME.
IT IS THE WILL OF ALLAH.

22:33.753 --> 22:36.055
AND I DO NOT FEAR
HIS DECISION.

22:36.088 --> 22:37.924
WELL, THEN WHAT SAY
WE FROG-MARCH
THIS BRAVE OLD MAN...

22:37.957 --> 22:41.327
AND HIS TWO FRIENDS OUT FRONT
AND BLOW THEIR BRAINS OUT
IN FRONT OF THEIR BUDDIES?

22:41.360 --> 22:44.230
BET THAT'D CHANGE
THIS SITUATION IN A HURRY,
WOULDN'T IT?

22:44.263 --> 22:46.232
HELL, WITHOUT HIM,
THEY'D PROBABLY
JUST PACK UP AND LEAVE!

22:46.265 --> 22:48.901
[ Laughs ]

22:48.935 --> 22:51.203
A COWARD THINKS
ALL OTHER MEN ARE COWARDS.

22:51.237 --> 22:54.206
AND A THIEF BELIEVES
ALL OTHERS ARE THIEVES!

22:54.240 --> 22:56.409
BY GOD, I'LL DO IT NOW!

22:56.443 --> 22:58.044
[ Groans ]

22:58.077 --> 23:00.212
- SARGE, NO!
- [ Jonas ]
LISTEN TO HIM.

23:00.246 --> 23:03.315
THERE WILL BE NO SECOND CHANCE.

23:04.984 --> 23:07.286
SCREW IT.
[ Jonas ]
HERE!

23:09.088 --> 23:11.223
BUT YOU TRY IT AGAIN,
I'LL KILL YOU.

23:15.127 --> 23:18.798
SERGEANT MAJOR,
I THINK YOU BETTER
WATCH YOUR BACK.

23:18.831 --> 23:22.001
I WAS WITH HIM IN IRAQ,
AND HE'S DONE SOME--

23:22.835 --> 23:25.605
JUST BE CAREFUL
IS ALL I'M SAYING.

23:25.638 --> 23:28.274
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

23:28.307 --> 23:31.310
YEAH, WELL, YOU BETTER
GET BACK ON THAT RADIO...

23:31.343 --> 23:33.713
AND TRY TO BREAK UP
SOME OF THAT STATIC.
SIR.

23:33.746 --> 23:36.048
EVEN A BLIND HOG GETS
AN ACORN EVERY NOW AND AGAIN.

23:36.082 --> 23:38.618
WILCO, SERGEANT MAJOR.

23:39.652 --> 23:42.088
MOST DIVERTING.

23:42.121 --> 23:43.823
YOU WOULD KILL ME
IF I TRIED TO ESCAPE,

23:43.856 --> 23:45.892
BUT YOU PROTECT ME
FROM A MURDERER.

23:45.925 --> 23:50.797
RIGHT. A CONDEMNED MAN
MUST BE KEPT HEALTHY
BEFORE HE CAN BE HUNG.

23:50.830 --> 23:52.665
IT IS YOUR LAW, YES?
IT IS THE LAW...

23:52.699 --> 23:55.434
THAT, AS MY PRISONER,
I'M BOUND TO PROTECT YOU.

23:55.468 --> 23:59.338
AN EXCELLENT LAW. WOULD THAT
MORE MEN OBSERVED IT.
[ Gunshots ]

24:01.774 --> 24:07.279
SOUNDS LIKE YOUR FRIENDS
OUT THERE ARE LEARNING THE LAW
OF EXTERIOR BALLISTICS.

24:11.851 --> 24:15.454
RANGE: 2,320 METERS!

24:16.789 --> 24:18.658
WINDAGE: RIGHT, FOUR MILLS.

24:25.532 --> 24:28.200
READY.
READY.

24:28.234 --> 24:32.404
[ Mack ]
AT MY COMMAND.
SNIPERS, READY, FIRE!

24:35.174 --> 24:38.144
ELEVATION AND WINDAGE,
NO CHANGE.

24:40.647 --> 24:43.415
[ Mack ]
SNIPERS, READY, FIRE!

24:45.918 --> 24:47.620
GOOD HIT! NO CHANGE!

24:47.654 --> 24:52.324
AMMO BOX.
SNIPERS, READY, FIRE!

24:57.163 --> 24:59.699
MISFIRE. YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN.

25:01.000 --> 25:03.636
THROUGH THE GRILLE, TWO ROUNDS!

25:03.670 --> 25:06.573
SNIPER, READY, FIRE!

25:10.577 --> 25:13.512
CEASE FIRE!

25:13.546 --> 25:16.115
[ All Cheering ]

25:17.617 --> 25:20.820
GREAT SHOOTING.
I'VE NEVER SEEN
ANYTHING LIKE THAT.

25:20.853 --> 25:24.323
GOT ABOUT AN HOUR AND A HALF
TILL SUNDOWN AND THERE'S STILL
A LOT OF WORK TO DO.

25:24.356 --> 25:27.760
LET'S NOT WASTE ANY OF IT.
LIEUTENANT.

25:27.794 --> 25:31.097
LIEUTENANT, LET'S MOVE
THOSE LIGHT SETS
TO THE CAMP INTERIOR.

25:31.130 --> 25:34.100
SERGEANT?
INDULGE ME, MA'AM.

25:46.278 --> 25:49.248
KNOCK THE PAIN DOWN FOR YA.
IT'LL TAKE A FEW MINUTES.

25:51.651 --> 25:53.419
OKAY, MA'AM. IT'S TIME.

25:54.921 --> 25:57.857
STAND TO, MEN!

25:57.890 --> 25:59.191
STAND TO!

25:59.225 --> 26:01.360
[ Man ]
STAND TO, MEN!
[ Man #2 ] STAND TO.

26:01.393 --> 26:03.562
[ Man #1 ] STAND TO!
[ Mack ]
STAND TO!

26:03.596 --> 26:05.564
[ Man #3 ]
STAND TO.

26:05.598 --> 26:08.134
[ Man #4 ]
STAND TO.

26:08.167 --> 26:10.136
[ Man #5 ]
STAND TO.

26:24.350 --> 26:28.287
** [ Man Singing
In Foreign Language ]

26:32.992 --> 26:35.127
THAT'S THE EVENING CALL
TO PRAYER.

26:38.364 --> 26:41.433
IF I SHOULD GO DOWN,
SERGEANT GERHARDT
WILL TAKE MY PLACE.

26:41.467 --> 26:44.771
AFTER HIM, GREY,
THEN WILLIAMS, THEN BROWN.

26:44.804 --> 26:49.108
BUT NO MATTER WHAT ELSE HAPPENS,
DO NOT LET WALLACE
NEAR THESE PRISONERS.

26:49.141 --> 26:53.012
RIGHT. YOU SIGN UP FOR R.O.T.C.
TO HELP PAY FOR COLLEGE.

26:53.045 --> 26:56.248
YOU JUST DON'T EVER THINK--
EVERYTHING WILL BE ALL RIGHT,
LIEUTENANT.

26:56.282 --> 26:59.118
YOU GOTTA BELIEVE THAT.
IF YOU BELIEVE IT,
SO WILL THE MEN.

26:59.151 --> 27:01.988
YES. I KNOW IT.

27:02.021 --> 27:05.825
WE'VE DONE EVERYTHING
WE POSSIBLY COULD. WE'RE READY.
YOU'RE DAMN RIGHT WE ARE.

27:05.858 --> 27:08.227
** [ Singing Continues ]

27:15.735 --> 27:18.370
[ Blaylock ]
ANY STATION. ANY STATION.
THIS IS OCEAN CEILING.

27:18.404 --> 27:21.841
DO YOU READ?
ANY STATION. ANY STATION.

27:21.874 --> 27:23.609
OKAY, MA'AM.
STAND-TO'S OVER.

27:23.642 --> 27:26.278
LET'S GET TO 50% SECURITY
UNTIL SOMETHING HAPPENS.

27:26.312 --> 27:29.481
I'LL GIVE THE ORDER.
LOOK. OVER THERE.

27:29.515 --> 27:31.984
[ Blaylock ] DO YOU READ?
[ Jonas ]
HUH. LANTERNS AND FLASHLIGHTS.

27:32.018 --> 27:33.619
THEY'RE COMING DOWN.
WHAT THE HELL?

27:33.652 --> 27:36.823
OH, THEY'RE MOVING ABOUT.
THEY'RE JUST TRYING
TO RATTLE US.

27:36.856 --> 27:39.859
- TELL THE MEN TO STAND FAST
AND WATCH THEIR SECTORS.
- [ Wallace ] ALL RIGHT.

27:39.892 --> 27:42.228
AND SEND OUT
THOSE LISTENING POSTS.
OKAY.

27:42.261 --> 27:44.363
ALL RIGHT, L.T.
I'M GONNA MOVE IN
AMONG THE MEN.

27:44.396 --> 27:48.067
I SUGGEST YOU STAY AT THE C.P.
WHERE WE ALL KNOW
WE CAN REACH YOU.

27:48.100 --> 27:50.136
THERE'S A CHANCE THOSE RADIOS
WILL COME TO LIFE.

27:50.169 --> 27:52.171
IF THEY DO,
YOU CAN CALL IT IN
FOR SOME SUPPORT.

27:53.172 --> 27:55.241
[ Gunshots ]
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

27:56.943 --> 27:59.045
[ Machine Gun Fire ]
CEASE FIRE!

28:01.380 --> 28:02.849
CEASE FIRE!
[ Bob ]
CEASE FIRE!

28:02.882 --> 28:05.051
- STOP THAT MACHINE GUN!
- [ Man ]
CEASE FIRE!

28:05.084 --> 28:07.920
[ Man #2 ]
CEASE FIRE! CEASE FIRE!

28:07.954 --> 28:10.289
[ Groans ]

28:12.691 --> 28:14.827
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

28:14.861 --> 28:17.163
MEDIC!
SHUT UP!

28:17.196 --> 28:19.398
IT WAS A PROBE TO GET US
TO SHOW OUR GUN POSITIONS.

28:19.431 --> 28:21.934
GET SOME HELP,
BUT DO IT QUIETLY.

28:21.968 --> 28:24.370
AND NO MORE SHOOTING
UNTIL I SAY SO.

28:24.403 --> 28:27.006
THE TROOPS
ARE SPOOKED ALREADY.
WELL, WE GOTTA UN-SPOOK 'EM.

28:27.039 --> 28:30.442
GET ANOTHER CREW ON THAT GUN.
TELL THEM DON'T SHOOT UNTIL
THEY ATTACK US IN THE WIRE.

28:30.476 --> 28:33.880
THE SIGNAL WILL BE
TWO GREEN STAR CLUSTERS.
WILL DO.

28:33.913 --> 28:36.215
I'M GONNA GIVE HECTOR
AND HIS CREW SOME WORK.

28:41.954 --> 28:43.722
PASS THE WORD
TO THE SQUAD LEADERS.

28:43.756 --> 28:46.725
NO MORE MACHINE GUN FIRE
AND NO MORE RIFLE FIRE
UNTIL ORDERED.

28:46.759 --> 28:50.396
THEY'RE TRYING TO GET A FIX
ON OUR POSITION SO THEY CAN
FIGURE OUT WHERE TO CRAWL UP TO.

28:50.429 --> 28:53.265
RIGHT. I'LL GO NOW.
L.T., TELL THE TROOPS...

28:53.299 --> 28:55.401
THE NEXT SOUND THEY HEAR
OUT THERE WILL BE OURS.

28:55.434 --> 28:57.736
- IT'LL BE A CROWD-PLEASER.
- ROGER THAT, SERGEANT MAJOR.

28:57.770 --> 28:59.138
MA'AM.
YES?

28:59.171 --> 29:01.673
DON'T FORGET TO SMILE.
IT REASSURES THE TROOPS.

29:03.475 --> 29:05.644
GOT IT.

29:05.677 --> 29:07.579
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

29:07.613 --> 29:10.282
- [ Jonas ]
PROBING FIRE.
- THOUGHT SO.

29:10.316 --> 29:12.718
LET'S GIVE 'EM A SURPRISE.
I WANT YOU TO FIRE
AN OPEN SHEATH.

29:12.751 --> 29:16.455
9:00 AND 12:00.
FOUR ROUNDS PER TUBE.

29:16.488 --> 29:19.091
WANNA WATCH?
NAH, I GOT
OTHER THINGS TO DO.

29:19.125 --> 29:21.627
GIVE ME FIVE MINUTES,
THEN LET HER RIP.

29:21.660 --> 29:23.462
[ Speaking Spanish ]

29:23.495 --> 29:26.665
ALPHA TEAM AT 9:00.
BRAVO TEAM AT 12:00.

29:26.698 --> 29:29.435
FOUR ROUNDS.
H.E. RANGE: 100 METERS,

29:29.468 --> 29:32.638
AND ADJUST OUTWARD
25 METERS PER ROUND.

29:32.671 --> 29:35.041
AT MY COMMAND.

29:38.310 --> 29:40.779
BOYS ARE GETTING JUMPY.
WELL, LET'S SETTLE 'EM DOWN.

29:40.813 --> 29:43.615
IN A COUPLE OF MINUTES,
HECTOR'S GONNA GIVE THEM
A LITTLE SURPRISE.

29:43.649 --> 29:48.454
WHEN HE DOES, FIRE A PARACHUTE
FLARE AND HAVE YOUR BOYS
SHOOT WHATEVER THEY SEE.

29:48.487 --> 29:51.157
I'M GONNA DO THE SAME THING
WITH THE FIRST SQUAD.

29:57.830 --> 29:59.966
[ Men Shouting
In Foreign Language ]

29:59.999 --> 30:02.634
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

30:02.668 --> 30:04.170
[ All Shouting ]

30:06.505 --> 30:08.007
FIRE!

30:21.187 --> 30:24.690
OVER THERE.
[ Groans ]

30:24.723 --> 30:26.725
[ Screaming ]

30:29.428 --> 30:31.163
[ Groans ]

30:50.016 --> 30:51.650
[ All Shouting ]

30:51.683 --> 30:54.420
[ Machine Gun Fire Continues ]

30:54.453 --> 30:57.423
[ Jonas ]
CEASE FIRE!
[ Shouting Continues ]

30:58.690 --> 31:00.526
[ Man ]
CAN'T SEE 'EM.

31:00.559 --> 31:02.561
[ Men Shouting
In Foreign Language ]

31:02.594 --> 31:06.298
[ Man ]
GOT NOTHING HERE!
[ Man #2 ] ANY MOVEMENT?

31:10.802 --> 31:13.605
[ Groans ]

31:13.639 --> 31:16.508
YOU CAN THANK GOD
AND THE AMERICAN TAXPAYERS
FOR THE BODY ARMOR.

31:16.542 --> 31:19.078
IT SAVED YOUR LIFE.
[ Chuckles, Groans ]

31:19.111 --> 31:21.213
I FEEL LIKE I'VE
BEEN HIT BY A TRUCK.

31:21.247 --> 31:23.749
A.K. ROUND STRAIGHT ON
WILL DO THAT TO YA.

31:23.782 --> 31:26.618
A COUPLE BROKEN RIBS TO BOOT.

31:26.652 --> 31:29.555
SERGEANT MAJOR,

31:29.588 --> 31:31.557
I WAS STUPID.
NO.

31:31.590 --> 31:33.592
IT'S CALLED COMBAT.

31:33.625 --> 31:36.695
YOU JUST STEPPED IN
THE FLIGHT PATH OF SOME BULLETS.
IT HAPPENS.

31:36.728 --> 31:39.966
WELL, YOU'RE OFFICIALLY
IN CHARGE NOW.

31:39.999 --> 31:42.734
WHAT HAPPENED?
[ Sighs ]
LIEUTENANT GOT HIT.

31:42.768 --> 31:45.904
- [ Groans ]
- THE SERGEANT MAJOR
IS IN COMMAND NOW.

31:45.938 --> 31:48.607
YES, MA'AM. I CAN SEE THAT.

31:48.640 --> 31:52.111
- WE REALLY KICKED
THEIR ASSES THAT TIME, HUH?
- IT WAS A PROBE.

31:52.144 --> 31:54.913
THEY FOUND OUT
WHAT THEY NEEDED TO KNOW.

31:54.947 --> 31:57.116
THEY'LL BE BACK.

31:57.149 --> 32:00.119
WHEN THEY'RE READY.
THEY'RE PROBABLY
GETTING INTO POSITION.

32:02.754 --> 32:04.656
RIGHT BEFORE
THE FLARE WENT OUT,

32:04.690 --> 32:07.659
I SAW ABOUT 40 MEN RUNNING
ALONG THE BASE OF THE HILL
ON MY SIDE.

32:07.693 --> 32:10.562
YOU CAN PROBABLY MULTIPLY THAT
BY A FACTOR OF THREE.

32:10.596 --> 32:14.166
OH, THAT'S OVER A HUNDRED MEN!
WE CAN'T POSSIBLY HOLD OUT
AGAINST THOSE ODDS!

32:14.200 --> 32:17.069
YES, WE CAN.
WE'RE DUG IN.
WE GOT PLENTY OF AMMO.

32:17.103 --> 32:19.471
GOOD FIELDS OF FIRE.
AND THE MEN ARE READY.

32:19.505 --> 32:22.841
WE JUST HAVE TO REMAIN CALM
AND DON'T PANIC.

32:22.874 --> 32:24.776
'CAUSE PANIC IS WHAT KILLS.

32:24.810 --> 32:27.246
RIGHT.

32:27.279 --> 32:30.949
SERGEANT WALLACE, I WANT YOU
TO TAKE OVER IN THE C.P.

32:30.983 --> 32:33.252
KEEP TRYING
TO MAKE RADIO CONTACT.

32:33.285 --> 32:36.455
SERGEANT GERHARDT'S GONNA
TAKE OVER AS PLATOON SERGEANT.

32:36.488 --> 32:38.290
YOU CAN MOVE OUT NOW.

32:42.995 --> 32:44.963
YOU'LL BE SAFE
HERE NOW, MA'AM.

32:44.997 --> 32:48.500
I'M SURE.
HAND ME MY RIFLE ANYWAY.

32:58.744 --> 33:00.879
SEE YOU IN THE MORNING, L.T.

33:00.912 --> 33:03.649
[ Groans ]
[ Mack ]
WHEN DO YOU THINK?

33:03.682 --> 33:07.819
HMM. AFTER MIDNIGHT.
THEY NEED TO GET INTO POSITION,

33:07.853 --> 33:09.788
LET US RELAX OUR GUARD.

33:09.821 --> 33:11.623
WELL, THEY GOTTA OVERRUN US.

33:11.657 --> 33:14.293
THAT'S ABOUT
THE ONLY CHANCE THEY GOT.
I SUSPECT SO.

33:14.326 --> 33:16.895
PUT THE TROOPS
ON 50% SECURITY.

33:16.928 --> 33:18.664
LET 'EM GET
AS MUCH REST AS POSSIBLE.

33:18.697 --> 33:20.999
THEY'LL WAKE UP
WHEN THE SHOOTING STARTS.
RIGHT.

33:21.033 --> 33:24.002
I'M GONNA DELIVER
ANOTHER BASIC LOAD OF AMMO
AND GET THEIR WATER TOPPED UP.

33:24.036 --> 33:27.639
AND LET 'EM KNOW
IF THEY NEED TO TAKE A LEAK,
DO IT IN THEIR FOXHOLES.

33:27.673 --> 33:31.210
THE ONLY FRIENDLIES I WANT
MOVING AROUND ARE THE LEADERS.
I WILL.

33:31.243 --> 33:33.545
HEY.

33:33.579 --> 33:35.547
IT'S GONNA GET UGLY.

33:35.581 --> 33:38.450
YEAH. I KNOW.

33:42.921 --> 33:45.857
ONE OF YOU KICK BACK,
GET SOME SHUT-EYE.

33:45.891 --> 33:47.559
YOU FIRST.
YES, SARGE.

33:55.634 --> 33:57.636
[ Chattering ]

33:59.738 --> 34:02.874
MACHINE GUNS KNOW NOT TO FIRE
TILL THE ENEMY HITS THE FINAL
PROTECTIVE LINE?

34:02.908 --> 34:05.244
THEY KNOW.
BUT WILL THEY DO?

34:05.277 --> 34:07.113
WELL, WE'LL SEE, WON'T WE?
HEY, WHAT TIME YOU GOT?

34:07.146 --> 34:09.081
WHY? TAKING MEDICINE?

34:10.949 --> 34:13.719
[ Man ]
INCOMING!
[ Groans ]

34:13.752 --> 34:15.654
DAMN IT!
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

34:18.890 --> 34:22.728
[ All Shouting ]
[ Foreign Language ]

34:22.761 --> 34:24.463
[ Machine Gun Fire Continues ]

34:26.064 --> 34:28.867
[ Man ]
FORWARD FIRE.
[ Man #2 ] ON THE RIDGE!

34:28.900 --> 34:31.937
[ Men Shouting ]

34:31.970 --> 34:34.240
AIMED SHOTS, MEN!
MAKE 'EM COUNT!

34:46.518 --> 34:49.988
YOU GOT ANY FLARES LEFT?
I JUST TOSSED THE LAST ONE.

34:50.956 --> 34:53.159
MACHINE GUNS NOW!

34:57.129 --> 35:00.166
CYCLIC RATE. HOLD IT DOWN.
[ Man ]
ON THE HILL!

35:16.982 --> 35:18.984
[ Jonas ]
CEASE FIRE!

35:19.017 --> 35:20.952
CEASE FIRE!
[ Man ]
CEASE FIRE!

35:20.986 --> 35:23.922
CEASE FIRE!
CEASE FIRE!

35:23.955 --> 35:26.925
CHECK THE LINE.
RECONSOLIDATE.

35:26.958 --> 35:29.161
CIRCULATE AMONG THE TROOPS.
CALM 'EM DOWN.

35:29.195 --> 35:32.598
AND THEN GET 'EM BACK
TO 50% SECURITY.

35:32.631 --> 35:36.435
WE JUST MAY HOLD THIS
THING TILL DAWN.
YEAH. OKAY.

35:36.468 --> 35:38.504
- WHERE DO YOU WANT THESE MEN?
- WHERE'D THEY COME FROM?

35:38.537 --> 35:40.939
WHAT THE HELL?
THERE WAS NOTHING
GOING ON BACK THERE.

35:40.972 --> 35:43.709
I FIGURED
THEY WERE NEEDED HERE.

35:43.742 --> 35:47.012
- YOU PULLED THESE MEN
OFF THE LINE?
- WELL, ONLY HALF OF THEM.

35:47.045 --> 35:49.715
TAKE THEM BACK
TO THEIR POSITIONS!
TAKE THEM BACK NOW!

35:49.748 --> 35:51.850
[ Mack ]
THEY'RE IN THE WIRE!

35:51.883 --> 35:55.254
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

36:06.598 --> 36:08.667
[ Man Shouts ]

36:08.700 --> 36:11.036
[ Man Shouts ]
GRENADE!

36:15.674 --> 36:18.644
[ Man ]
I'M HIT!
[ Explosion ]

36:18.677 --> 36:20.712
MEDIC!

36:21.613 --> 36:23.882
MEDIC!

36:23.915 --> 36:26.051
[ Men Shouting ]
[ Machine Gun Fire ]

36:36.462 --> 36:39.265
FIRE THE F.P.L.!

36:40.031 --> 36:42.268
FIRE THE F.P.L.!

36:58.450 --> 37:00.386
[ Groans ]

37:03.989 --> 37:07.293
FALL BACK! FALL BACK
TO THE ALTERNATE POSITION!

37:08.494 --> 37:10.796
FALL BACK TO THE DITCH, MEN!
FALL BACK!

37:10.829 --> 37:13.532
[ Mack ]
FALL BACK, MEN!
BACK TO THE DITCH!

37:13.565 --> 37:17.135
END OF THE LINE, MEN!
HIGH-ANGLE, FIRE!

37:36.588 --> 37:39.257
[ All Shouting ]

37:39.291 --> 37:42.127
[ Man ]
RELOAD!
FALL BACK!

37:42.160 --> 37:44.330
FALL BACK!
WE'RE FALLING BACK!

37:51.036 --> 37:52.971
[ Man ]
RELOAD IT!

38:01.347 --> 38:04.282
ANY STATION! ANY STATION!
THIS IS OCEAN CEILING.

38:04.316 --> 38:07.453
WE ARE UNDER HEAVY ATTACK!
ANY STATION! ANY STATION!

38:07.486 --> 38:09.988
RESPOND! OVER?

38:10.021 --> 38:12.123
NOTHING, SARGE!
DAMN IT.

38:12.157 --> 38:14.593
JOHNSON, TAKE COX
AND CARTER WITH YOU.

38:14.626 --> 38:17.429
GO GET THOSE DAMN PRISONERS
OUT OF THE CAGE
AND BRING 'EM HERE!

38:17.463 --> 38:20.832
I KNOW HOW TO PUT
AN END TO THIS.
DO IT NOW, DAMN IT!

38:20.866 --> 38:22.968
AND BRING 'EM TO ME!

38:23.001 --> 38:24.135
ANY STATION! ANY STATION!

38:24.169 --> 38:26.672
[ Man ]
FALL BACK!
FALL BACK!

38:26.705 --> 38:30.342
[ Man Shouts ]

38:30.376 --> 38:32.378
[ Groans ]

38:34.380 --> 38:35.547
COME ON! OUT!

38:35.581 --> 38:37.315
YOU HEARD ME! OUT!

38:37.349 --> 38:39.618
MACK!

38:39.651 --> 38:41.987
FIRE!

38:43.321 --> 38:44.990
FIRE!

38:45.357 --> 38:48.326
FIRE!

39:08.547 --> 39:11.082
THE PRISONERS! THE PRISONERS!
WHAT ABOUT THE PRISONERS,
DAMN IT?

39:11.116 --> 39:13.719
THEY'RE LOOSE,
AND THEY HAVE OUR WEAPONS!

39:13.752 --> 39:16.054
GOD ALMIGHTY.

39:22.594 --> 39:24.596
LIGHTS!

39:26.798 --> 39:29.568
[ Groans ]

39:29.601 --> 39:32.638
IT'S THE PRISONERS!
THEY'VE GOTTEN LOOSE,
AND THEY'VE GOT GUNS!

39:33.572 --> 39:35.607
GIVE ME A HAND HERE!

39:35.641 --> 39:37.976
[ Man Shouts ]

39:51.957 --> 39:55.360
STAY DOWN!
KEEP THEM DOWN!

39:55.393 --> 39:57.128
DOWN!

40:02.133 --> 40:04.102
IT'S GOTTA STOP!
WE GOTTA MAKE IT STOP!

40:04.135 --> 40:06.037
WE GOTTA COUNTERATTACK!

40:06.071 --> 40:08.139
TOO LATE FOR THAT!
THEY'LL KILL US ALL!

40:12.844 --> 40:15.146
BY GOD, HE GOES FIRST.

40:16.482 --> 40:18.717
NO!

40:18.750 --> 40:21.453
AAAH!

40:21.487 --> 40:23.589
[ Groaning ]

40:24.923 --> 40:26.892
PUT THAT
ON YOUR LEG.
YOU!

40:26.925 --> 40:29.160
MAYBE YOU'LL LIVE.

40:30.629 --> 40:33.431
[ Jonas ]
KEEP FIRING!

40:33.465 --> 40:35.300
INTO THEM!

40:35.333 --> 40:37.335
[ Groans ]

40:44.309 --> 40:46.512
[ Man ]
I'M HIT!

40:46.545 --> 40:49.447
MEDIC! MEDIC!

40:52.283 --> 40:56.287
COME ON, MEN!
YOU WANT TO LIVE FOREVER?

40:56.321 --> 40:58.123
GO! GO!

40:59.457 --> 41:01.459
[ All Shouting ]

41:08.534 --> 41:11.169
[ Shouting Continues ]

41:25.483 --> 41:27.452
THEY'RE GONE.

41:27.485 --> 41:29.354
LEADERS, CONSOLIDATE.

41:29.387 --> 41:32.691
REDISTRIBUTE
ARMS AND AMMUNITION.

41:32.724 --> 41:34.492
MAINTAIN POSITIONS.

41:46.071 --> 41:48.173
HOW MANY DEAD?
[ Williams ]
TOO MANY.

41:53.444 --> 41:55.581
WHERE'S THE L.T.?
OVER HERE.

41:57.182 --> 42:00.351
HOW YOU DOING?
I'M ALL RIGHT.
WHAT'S THE STATUS?

42:00.385 --> 42:03.088
WELL, THEY SLIPPED BACK
INTO THE HILLS.
WE HURT 'EM PRETTY BAD.

42:03.121 --> 42:05.156
- BUT ANOTHER NIGHT
LIKE TONIGHT--
- RADIO'S ALIVE!

42:05.190 --> 42:06.758
I MADE CONTACT
WITH HEADQUARTERS.

42:06.792 --> 42:09.494
THEY'RE SENDING A MEDEVAC
AND A RELIEF UNIT.
BE HERE IN 20.

42:09.527 --> 42:11.429
THEN WE MADE IT.

42:11.462 --> 42:13.464
LOOKS THAT WAY.

42:14.700 --> 42:18.536
HEY, TOP. OVER HERE.

42:37.889 --> 42:40.225
[ Flies Buzzing ]
DEAD.

42:40.258 --> 42:42.260
ALL THREE.

42:42.293 --> 42:44.295
YEAH.

42:49.901 --> 42:52.037
BUT WHAT--

42:52.070 --> 42:54.039
WHO DID IT?

42:54.072 --> 42:56.141
THEM. US. WHO KNOWS?

43:05.984 --> 43:08.586
AND WHO THE HELL
WAS HE ANYWAY...

43:09.520 --> 43:11.657
THAT CAUSED ALL OF THIS?

43:11.690 --> 43:14.559
[ Jonas ]
A MAN.

43:14.592 --> 43:16.427
IT'S JUST A MAN.

43:28.306 --> 43:30.208
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

43:37.482 --> 43:40.051
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP **
